This directory contains Sather classes implementing a variety of 
connectionist networks and algorithms.

README: This file.

TEST.sa: Test all connectionist classes: CONNECTIONIST_CLASSES_TEST.

feed_forward_net.sa: General feed-forward networks and versions 
   trainable by back-propagation: FEED_FORWARD_NET, BACK_PROP, 
   FEED_FORWARD_NET_TEST, BACK_PROP_TEST.

